t heaviness—leaving hair clean, soft, and ready to grow.<br\/><\/p><p><br\/>Strengthens hair to support long-term growth retention<br\/><br\/>With continued use, strands stay stronger, smoother, and more resilient, helping you finally keep the length you gain.<\/p>","question_4":"RADIANT ROOT RISK FREE GUARANTEE","answer_4":"<p>We want you to feel completely confident in your purchase.<\/p><p>That’s why every order is backed by our 60-day money-back guarantee.<\/p><p>If your item arrives damaged or defective, we’ll make it right with a replacement or full refund.<\/p><p>To start a return or exchange, simply contact our customer support team within 60 days of delivery. Share your order number and a quick description of the issue, and we’ll guide you through the process quickly and hassle-free.<\/p><p>Your satisfaction is our priority. We stand behind every product we make and are committed to delivering high-quality formulas and exceptional customer care.<\/p>","question_5":"","answer_5":"","question_6":"","answer_6":"","question_7":"","answer_7":"","question_8":"","answer_8":"","question_9":"","answer_9":"","question_10":"","answer_10":""}},"video_carousel_standalone_xw3T8p":{"type":"video_carousel_standalone","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"See it in action","heading_size":24,"heading_color":"#211a28","scrollbar_color":"#211a28","disable_sound_controls":true,"enable_autoplay":true,"show_sound_controls_autoplay":false,"play_button_size":30,"sound_button_size":30,"play_button_bg_color":"#000000","play_button_bg_opacity":35,"sound_button_bg_color":"#000000","sound_button_bg_opacity":35,"hide_scrollbar":true,"video_size":260,"show_social_badge":true,"social_platform":"instagram","view_count":3.4,"badge_text":"Over","badge_suffix":"M Views On Instagram","use_gradient_text":true,"badge_background_color":"#ffffff","badge_text_color":"#211a28","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0}},"customer_review_XcjYbg":{"type":"customer_review","disabled":true,"settings":{"reviewer_